    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Alright! This should be plenty."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "*Cough* *Wheeze*... Talk about using people..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "What should we do, Sophie? Want to look around a little more?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x1c,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Huh!? No way, that's enough! I'm exhausted..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x1e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "And if we stick around too long, some dangerous monsters could appear."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Hm, Oskar might be right..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Okay then, let's head back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. Oh, both of you should drop by the atelier. I'll make tea for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Oh really? Then we'll take you up on that offer. Right, Oskar?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Y-yeah... But first, let me catch my breath..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Would you like to view the explanation for changes in gathering fields?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Taking actions outside of town consumes LP."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Losing LP will reduce your abilities. Try to avoid battles while low on LP."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Also, exploring the same field multiple times will allow you to gather better materials."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "However, the enemies will also grow stronger, so be careful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "The time and weather can also affect the materials you gather, and the monsters that appear."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You can view more details about field changes under Help in the Encyclopedia."
        }
    ]
}